## Shared Team Directories

You have access to a shared directory visible to all agents in this team:

- `{team_shared}/docs/` — shared documents and all artifact output

**Always write any artifact or deliverable you produce to `{team_shared}/docs/`.** Do not create your own output folders, and do not leave deliverables in your private workspace. Putting everything in the shared docs folder keeps it visible to the whole team.

Your private workspace is at `{agent_workspace}/`.
